  "description": "A nighttime long shot of a cityscape illuminated by fireworks. The scene features a long bridge with moving vehicle lights stretching across dark water, leading towards a dense urban skyline. Numerous buildings are lit with golden and white lights, creating a vibrant contrast against the dark sky. Fireworks explode in the distance, adding bursts of bright white and red to the composition. The overall perspective is from a high vantage point, providing a wide view of the city and surrounding area. The water reflects some of the city lights, creating a shimmering effect.",
